data.description: COME FALL IN LOVE WITH THIS COUNTRY GEM!  Are you ready to get out of the city?  Here's your chance!  Come check out this 3 bed, 1 1/2 bath glorious ranch home with a large 1-acre yard.  It's just what you've been waiting for!  Spacious and inviting open floor plan with high ceilings. Large eat-in kitchen with stainless steel appliances and lots of cabinet space. Vinyl plank flooring throughout the kitchen and family room.  Perfect for pets.  The three large bedrooms boast new carpet, lots of closet space and is ready for your family to move right in.  The unfinished basement could be easily converted into more living space and another bedroom.  This home has too many updates to mention them all.  Like appliances, electrical, plumbing, gutters with gutter guards, newer furnace, water heater, roof, perimeter drains, siding, sump pump and many more.  South Putnam school district.  This home will not last long.  Hurry, schedule your private showing today!!
